msgid "Tetsuo made a noble sacrifice."
msgstr "Tetsuo hizo un noble sacrificio."

msgid "Tetsuo's investigation has failed."
msgstr "la investigación de Tetsuo fracasó."

msgid "the investigators saved the mutated officer."
msgstr "los investigadores salvaron al policía mutado."

